reviewText: Everything came fine.
Love it

Sent off for 3 disc dvd and recieved  a VHS tape and wrong Movie to boot!!! Too much hassle for the few dollars I spent to try to return it so will re-order the dvd from someone else. Was it a human error? Was it product description error? Who knows, I only know I got the wrong movie...Not mad...just dissapointed...

This set contains 2 DVDs of the Colgate Comedy Hour (9 episodes total) featuring Dean Martin and Jerry Lewis, the funniest comedy duo of all time. A DVD of At War With The Army is also included. The episodes include guests Helen O'Connell, Dorothy Dandridge, Rosemary Clooney, and more. Being a HUGE Jerry Lewis fan, I am biased, but I definitely thought it was worth the money for this collection of laughs.

The Martin & Lewis Colgate Comedy Hour was only on for a short time.  Younger viewers owe it to themselves to watch these timeless sketches that only M&L could deliver.
Oh for the 50's again - without Korean war!
